===A maḍal n w'aɛraben akk d ye nselmen===
[[Tugna:Image-Al-Kitāb_al-muḫtaṣar_fī_ḥisāb_al-ğabr_wa-l-muqābala.jpg|thumb|120px| A sebtar n ''Aljiber'' n [[Abou Jafar Muhammad Ibn Mūsa al-Khuwārizmī|el-Khwarizmi]]]]


'''Aljiber''' yekk'd deg [[taɛrabt]] al-ǧabr, yuqal ''algebra'' s [[Ta latinit|te latinit]], anamek is yezzi ugar ɣer '''A sdakel'''(la reunion) n i ceqqfan, neɣ '''tuqqna''' (la connexion). Akken daɣen ig wwi i numak(sens) nniḍen deg [[Tutlayt|tutlayin]] nniḍen.

D'awal ig llan ger w'awalen i mezwura i sqedcen s tutlayt taɛrabt,  adlis id yessufeɣ [[Abou Jafar Muhammad Ibn Mūsa al-Khuwārizmī|el-Khwarizmi]] isemma-y-as [[al-ǧabr wa el mouqabalah]], izrew dges aṭṭas n [[Ta nzeggit|te nzeggit]] , i wumi ass agi leqdic ines nessemlal it ugar ɣer [[Ta nzeggit taljibrit|te nzeggit taljibrit]].

Yiwet tikkelt [[Leonardo Fibonacci|Leonard de Pise]] i win mi qqaren [[Leonardo Fibonacci|Fibonacci]] yerza ɣer [[Tafriqt ugafa| te friqt n we gafa]], ira(aimer) amek ttarun [[Azwil|i zwilen ]] deg tama agi n we maḍal, deg imir yesseqdac i zwilen akini, yerna yewwiten id ɣer [[Turuft|europa]].

